  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to change the concentration of amyloid-beta in human
      cerebrospinal fluid (CSF) by modification of sleep efficiency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to investigate whether or not increasing sleep efficiency will
      change the concentration of amyloid-beta in cerebrospinal fluid (CSF).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
